-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/1ce4c1fa-9c37-431e-a5b8-236462f5ca3a.png\"/>  (4)\n<br>Từ (3) và (4), suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/02c3e4bd-5e72-44f1-ab7a-e48dcb9045d7.png\"/> là hình bình hành\n<br>Hơn nữa, <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/8a3606c5-6b19-4b3f-9d73-92cb4ef22468.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra, <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/abade281-8a91-4e76-8fcd-d071ee9821a7.png\"/> là hình chữ nhật\n<br>Nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/02c91fdd-e357-47dd-8f62-fa8b7c32ea93.png\"/>\n<br>d) Xét tam giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/b8b5d318-2f64-46b2-b696-75b687e62df6.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/ef3664c6-d2c6-49b8-bc53-de5b70d8a050.png\"/> ta có:\n<br>- <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/965b7d75-40a8-4799-9e5e-323b1e8dc4ae.png\"/>\n<br>- <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/7bb3343f-6c88-4b63-aa7c-e375ee1037f8.png\"/>\n<br>- <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/697ef318-0cb9-42c9-8b2d-98c971c639cd.png\"/> chung\n<br>Suy ra, <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/a2825ca8-611c-41a0-981e-4704c4595434.png\"/> (c-g-c)\n<br>Nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/41230115-d83f-428c-9f01-d8066d8d51d3.png\"/>\n<br>Mặt khác, tam giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/8399d34c-e7c4-4a79-ac12-acba9bfd2921.png\"/> cân tại <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/dba1a993-63